            "title": "9月期指最後成交价26535点　　升51点",
            "description": "<div id=\"newsBody\">\n<span class=\"newsDetail\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family:MingLiu;Arial;\">&lt;汇港通讯&gt;    9月期指最後成交价26535点，升51点，高水50点；10月期指最後成交价26580点，升51点，高水95点。</span>\n</div>",
            "pub_date": "2025-09-25 16:40:36",
